      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is increasingly rare in the pre-owned market. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, this specimen offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
